EXCLUSIVE: AHN GA-YEONG AND PATRICK DATING
DESPITE A 10-YEAR AGE GAP

267
00:21:03,595 --> 00:21:05,055
Come in.

268
00:21:15,315 --> 00:21:17,317
I read the news article.

269
00:21:19,236 --> 00:21:20,487
Are you okay?

270
00:21:25,867 --> 00:21:27,202
It's you, my friend.

271
00:21:27,911 --> 00:21:29,663
I thought it was one of my enemies.

272
00:21:31,373 --> 00:21:32,916
Were you worried about me?

273
00:21:34,501 --> 00:21:36,253
